➜泰国曼谷数万人示威游行，要求改革君主立宪制
http://www.sohu.com/a/419602680_313745	10709
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
